com.vanillasource.gerec

Class HttpStatusCode

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vanillasource.gerec.HttpStatusCode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public final class HttpStatusCode
extends Object
implements Serializable
    A list of HTTP status codes in a quasi-enumeration. HTTP Codes are almost an enumeration, except they can (and are) extended with new specifications. So this class defines constant objects which can be used with the '==' sign, and can be used in switch statements normally, but also are able to contain values which were not previously defined.
